%div{ :id => "home" }
	%section
		%div{ :class => "container" }
			%div{ :class => "row"}
				%div{ :class => "col-md-offset-4 col-md-8" }
					%h1{ :class => "orange slogan" } 
						Hello,
						I'm Luchia.
					%p{ :class => "grey" } Scroll down to learn more.

%div{ :id => "about" }
	%div{ :class => "container" }
		%div{ :id => "text-container" }
			%h1{ :class => "white text-center italic" } 
				I'm a designer who likes to develop too - yep, multi-talented.
			%br
			%div{ :class => "row" }
				%div{ :class => "col-md-4" }
					%h3 Digital Design
					%p{ :class => "grey" }
						Digital design is my passion and I specialise in Branding Identities and Website Design. I enjoy creating modern, timeless identities that will serve my clients without becoming out of fashion.
				%div{ :class => "col-md-4" }
					%h3 Web Development
					%p{ :class => "grey" }
						I build clean, professional and responsive websites. I believe in designing mobile first and create beautiful websites with great content architecture. I'm working Ruby on Rails, HTML5 & CSS3 at the moment.
				%div{ :class => "col-md-4" }
					%h3 Photography
					%p{ :class => "grey" }
						I've been behind the lense since I was 12 years old - composing a great photo is an obsession that I can't get over. I love candid-style photos and shoot weddings, fashion and every day life.

%div{ :id => "work" }
	%div{ :class => "container" }
		%div{ :id => "text-container" }
			%section
				%div{ :class => "row" }
					-@portfolios.each do |portfolio|
						%div{ :class => "col-md-4" }
							%h3{ :class => "white" }
								%a{ :href => '/portfolios/'+portfolio.id.to_s }=portfolio.title
							%p{ :class => "grey" }=truncate(portfolio.content, length: 150)

				%p{ :class => "left-aligned white" }
					%br
					%br
					%a{ :href => "/work/" }
						See more

%div{ :id => "contact" }
	%div{ :class => "container" }
		%div{ :class => "pushdown" }
			%section
				%h3{ :class => "text-center italic" }
					%span{ :class => "brisbane" }
						Based in Brisbane, Australia.
						%a{ :href => "/contact" } 
							Interested?